'''密蘇里鏟鱘'''（[[學名|學名]]：''{{lang|la|Scaphirhynchus albus}}''），又名'''淺色鱘魚'''（英语：Pallid sturgeon），是原產於[[密蘇里河|密蘇里河]]及下[[密西西比河|密西西比河]]盆地的一種[[瀕危|瀕危]][[輻鰭魚|輻鰭魚]]。牠們如其名般色澤很淺，與[[扁吻鏟鱘|扁吻鏟鱘]]是近親，但身體較長。約長76-150厘米及重39公斤。<ref name="montana">{{cite web|title=Pallid Sturgeon - ''Scaphirhynchus albus''|publisher=Montana Fish, Wildlife and Parks|url=http://fwp.mt.gov/wildthings/tande/pallid.html|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081107171623/http://fwp.mt.gov/wildthings/tande/pallid.html|archivedate=2008-11-07}}</ref><ref name="Platte">{{cite web|title=The Pallid Sturgeon (''Scaphirhynchus albus'')|publisher=Platte River Endangered Species Partnership|url=http://www.platteriver.org/backgr/sturg.htm|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930003925/http://www.platteriver.org/backgr/sturg.htm|archivedate=2007-09-30}}</ref>牠們需要15年的時間才完全成長，而且也不經常產卵，但卻可以活上達100年。[[鱘科|鱘科]]最早可以追溯至7000萬年前的[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]，而淺色鱘魚一直沒有主要改變，可以說是一種由[[恐龍|恐龍]]時代留下來的遺跡。<ref name="dinosaur">{{cite web|title=The Pallid Sturgeon, a Missouri River "Dinosaur"|work=Feature Series, Vol I, No. 4|publisher=U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service|url=http://www.r6.fws.gov/feature/sturgeon.html|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081119020600/http://www.r6.fws.gov/feature/sturgeon.html|archivedate=2008-11-19}}</ref>

於1990年，[[美國魚類及野生動物管理局|美國漁業暨野生動物局]]將淺色鱘魚列為[[瀕危物種|瀕危物種]]。十年以來只發現有少量的幼魚，且很少再觀察到牠們的蹤跡。<ref name="endangered">{{cite web|title=Operation and Maintenance of the Upper Mississippi River 9-Foot Channel|work=Endangered Species Program|publisher=U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service|date=November 18, 2008|url=http://www.fws.gov/midwest/Endangered/section7/pallid.html|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2011-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110526224744/http://www.fws.gov/midwest/Endangered/section7/pallid.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>牠們是第一種密西西比河的[[魚類|魚類]]被列為瀕危。其衰落的主因相信是失去棲息地。大部份密西西比河的河道都被改道或築壩，適合淺色鱘魚產卵的砂礫河床及慢流側道都大幅減少。牠們的肉質美味，卵可以造成[[魚子醬|魚子醬]]。<ref name="NRCS">{{cite web|title=Threatened and Endangered Species: Pallid Sturgeon ''Scaphirhynchus'' Fact Sheet|publisher=U.S. Department of Agriculture|date=November 16, 2005|url=http://www.mt.nrcs.usda.gov/news/factsheets/pallidsturgeon.html|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20051126220804/http://www.mt.nrcs.usda.gov/news/factsheets/pallidsturgeon.html|archivedate=2005-11-26}}</ref> 

保育淺色鱘魚的工作得到了稍微的成功。每年也有約一打的淺色鱘魚從[[魚苗孵化場|魚苗孵化場]]放生到野外。為了了解淺色鱘魚的行為，研究人員植入了[[GPS|GPS]]發訊器來追蹤牠們的行動及尋找其產卵地。另外，也有工作改善牠們產卵地的環境，來增加其野外生存的機會。

==分類及命名==
Stephen Alfred Forbes及R. E. Richardson於1905年將淺色鱘魚分類在[[鏟鱘屬|鏟鱘屬]]及[[鱘科|鱘科]]下。密蘇里鏟鱘的近親是較為普遍的[[扁吻鏟鱘|扁吻鏟鱘]]及[[極危|極危]]的[[阿拉巴馬鏟鱘|阿拉巴馬鏟鱘]]。<ref name="AlabamaIUCN">{{IUCN2008|title=Scaphirhynchus suttkusi|assessors=Parauka, F.M.|year=2004|id=19942|downloaded=08 Dec 2008}}</ref><ref name="AlabamaSEFC">{{cite news|title=The Desperate Dozen: Fishes on the Brink|publisher=Southeastern Fishes Council|date=November 2008|url=http://www.flmnh.ufl.edu/fish/organizations/sfc/DesDoz_report.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-12-09|archive-date=2009-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225123602/http://www.flmnh.ufl.edu/fish/organizations/sfc/DesDoz_report.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>這三種魚都是屬於[[鏟鱘亞科|鏟鱘亞科]]。

淺色鱘魚一如其名的顏色較淺。<ref name="Guide">{{cite web|title=Pallid Sturgeon|work=Animal Field Guide|publisher=Montana Fish, Wildlife and Parks|url=http://fwp.mt.gov/fieldguide/detail_AFCAA02010.aspx|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081108123929/http://fwp.mt.gov/fieldguide/detail_AFCAA02010.aspx|archivedate=2008-11-08}}</ref>其[[種小名|種小名]]的[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]意思是「白色」。<ref name="Riis">{{cite web|last=Riis|first=Jim|title=Pallid Sturgeon (''Scaphirhynchus albus'')|publisher=South Dakota Department of Game, Fish and Parks|year=1993|url=http://www.northern.edu/natsource/ENDANG1/Pallid1.htm|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080206135111/http://www.northern.edu/natsource/ENDANG1/Pallid1.htm|archivedate=2008-02-06}}</ref>

==生物學==
===DNA===
早期的[[DNA|DNA]]研究認為密蘇里鏟鱘及[[扁吻鏟鱘|扁吻鏟鱘]]是同一[[物種|物種]]。<ref name="Tranah1">{{cite journal en|last=Tranah|first=G. J.|coauthors=D. E. Campton, and B. May|title=Genetic Evidence for Hybridization of Pallid and Shovelnose Sturgeon|journal=Journal of Heredity|volume=95|issue=6|pages=474–80|publisher=The American Genetic Association|date=2004|url=http://jhered.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/full/95/6/474|doi=10.1093/jhered/esh077|accessdate=2008-12-14|archive-date=2008-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080906223608/http://jhered.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/full/95/6/474|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是於2000年的研究，在比較所有三種[[鏟鱘屬|鏟鱘屬]]的[[DNA序列|DNA序列]]後，才發覺牠們分別為三個獨立的物種。<ref name="Campton">{{cite journal en|last=Campton|first=Donald E.|coauthors=Anna L. Bass, Frank A. Chapman and Brian W. Bowen|title=Genetic distinction of pallid, shovelnose, and Alabama sturgeon: emerging species and the US Endangered Species Act|journal=Conservation Genetics|volume=1|issue=1|pages=17–32|publisher=Springer Netherlands|date=March 2000|url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/w76485t849537674/|doi=10.1023/A:1010121417487|accessdate=2008-12-14}}{{Dead link|date=2020年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>2001年及2006年間的幾項研究發現在北部的淺色鱘魚是[[生殖隔離|生殖隔離]]的，且與[[路易西安納州|路易西安納州]][[阿查費耶拉河|阿查費耶拉河]]（Atchafalaya River）的南部群落在[[基因|基因]]上有所不同。不過這種不同並非是物種層級的。<ref name="Tranah2">{{cite journal en|last=Tranah|first=G. J.|coauthors=H. L. Kincaid, C. C. Krueger, D. E. Campton, and B. May|title=Reproductive isolation in sympatric populations of pallid and shovelnose sturgeon|journal=North American Journal of Fisheries Management|volume=21|pages=367–73|publisher=American Fisheries Society|date=March 2001|url=http://genome-lab.ucdavis.edu/Publications/2001TranahEtAl_NAJFM.pdf|accessdate=2008-11-19|doi=10.1577/1548-8675(2001)021<0367:RIISPO>2.0.CO;2|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225123603/http://genome-lab.ucdavis.edu/Publications/2001TranahEtAl_NAJFM.pdf|archivedate=2009-02-25}}</ref><ref name="Billings">{{cite web|title=Pallid Sturgeon (''Scaphirhynchus albus'') 5-Year Review Summary and Evaluation|publisher=U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service|date=2007|pages=24-28|url=http://www.uwyo.edu/enr/ienr/PSWorkshop2007/Pallid_Sturgeon_5year_Review_Final_June2007.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2009-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225123603/http://www.uwyo.edu/enr/ienr/PSWorkshop2007/Pallid_Sturgeon_5year_Review_Final_June2007.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

密蘇里鏟鱘的南部群落在[[密蘇里河|密蘇里河]]盆地中部與密西西比鏟鱘的[[混種|混種]]較多，而北部群落則較少。<ref name="Billings"/>在阿查費耶拉河有最多的混種。混種的基因與淺色鱘魚的不同，但與扁吻鏟鱘的無法區分。<ref name="Tranah2"/>混種是否能夠生殖仍未知。<ref name="Tranah1"/>

===特徵===
[[File:Pallid_Sturgeon_head_detail.JPG|thumb]]
淺色鱘魚是[[北美洲|北美洲]]最大的淡水魚之一。牠們一般長76-150厘米及重達39公斤。<ref name="montana"/><ref name="Platte"/>牠們自遠古時代已經存在，由7000萬年前的[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]至今也差不多沒有改變。<ref name="dinosaur"/>[[扁吻鏟鱘|扁吻鏟鱘]]雖然外表與淺色鱘魚很相似，但卻較為細小，一般最多只重2.3公斤。淺色鱘魚較為淡色，背部及側面呈灰白色，而密西西比鏟鱘則呈褐色。<ref name="NRCS"/>淺色鱘魚隨著年齡漸長會變得更白，而幼魚很易與扁吻鏟鱘混淆。<ref name="Missouri">{{cite web|title=Endangered Sturgeon Struggle for Survival|work=The Sturgeon of Missouri Missouri's Aquatic Dinosaurs|publisher=Conservation Commission of Missouri|year=2008|url=http://mdc.mo.gov/fish/sport/sturgeon/info/|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081203150314/http://www.mdc.mo.gov/fish/sport/sturgeon/info/|archivedate=2008-12-03}}</ref>淺色鱘魚是歪尾的，上尾鰭較長。<ref name="Johnsgard">{{cite book en|last=Johnsgard|first=Paul A.|title=The Nature of Nebraska|publisher=Bison Books|date=April 1, 2005|location=Lincoln, Nebraska|pages=169–70|id=ISBN 978-0803276215}}</ref>

淺色鱘魚沒有[[鱗片|鱗片]]或[[骨頭|骨頭]]，只有[[軟骨|軟骨]]骨骼。軟骨是五列的厚板，包裹大部份的[[頭部|頭部]]，一直沿兩側、底部及背部伸延至尾巴。<ref name="Riis"/>軟骨板有[[皮膚|皮膚]]覆蓋，可以作為保護裝甲。<ref name="Johnsgard"/>

淺色鱘魚的吻及頭部較扁吻鏟鱘長。<ref name="Missouri"/>口縮在較吻端後的位置。牠們沒有[[牙齒|牙齒]]，會伸長口部從河底吸入細小的[[魚類|魚類]]、[[軟體動物|軟體動物]]及其他食物。淺色鱘魚的吻部有四條鬚，相信是一種確定食物位置的感覺[[器官|器官]]。<ref name="Johnsgard"/>兩條內側的鬚只有外側的一半長<ref name="NRCS"/>，且位於較前端。

===繁殖及生命周期===
[[File:Juvenilepallid.jpg|thumb]]
淺色鱘魚非常長壽，可以活到50歲以上，甚至長達100歲。<ref name="NWF">{{cite web|title=Upper Missouri Pallid Sturgeon|publisher=National Wildlife Federation|url=http://www.nwf.org/endangered/pdfs/UM-PallidSturgeon.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090117185658/http://nwf.org/endangered/pdfs/UM-PallidSturgeon.pdf|archivedate=2009-01-17}}</ref><ref name="Burton">{{cite web|last=Burton|first=Ken|title=New Hope for the Pallid Sturgeon|work=Endangered Species Bulletin|publisher=U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service|date=January/April 2000|url=http://www.fws.gov/endangered//bulletin/2000/01-04/04-05.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2009-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225123624/http://www.fws.gov/endangered//bulletin/2000/01-04/04-05.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Gavins">{{cite web|title=Abnormal Cells found in Pallid Sturgeon at Gavins Point National Fish Hatchery Prohibit Stocking these Fish in the Wild|publisher=U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service|date=September 26, 2007|url=http://www.fws.gov/mountain-prairie/PRESSREl/07-61.htm|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2008-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081015050115/http://www.fws.gov/mountain%2Dprairie/pressrel/07-61.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於牠們沒有[[鱗片|鱗片]]及[[骨頭|骨頭]]，故很難確定牠們的年齡。<ref name="Holm">{{cite web|last=Holm|first=Rob|title=Prehistoric Presence The Pallid Sturgeon|publisher=North Dakota Outdoors|date=April–May 2002|url=http://gf.nd.gov/multimedia/ndoutdoors/issues/2002/apr-may/docs/sturgeon.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225123603/http://gf.nd.gov/multimedia/ndoutdoors/issues/2002/apr-may/docs/sturgeon.pdf|archivedate=2009-02-25}}</ref>淺色鱘魚的性成熟相對很遲才來到：<ref name="EPA">{{cite web|title=Status and Life History of the Pallid Sturgeon|publisher=U.S. Environmental Protection Agency|date=August 31, 2007|url=http://www.epa.gov/espp/litstatus/effects/appendix_c_life_history_sturgeon.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2009-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225123602/http://www.epa.gov/espp/litstatus/effects/appendix_c_life_history_sturgeon.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>雄魚約到5-7歲就達至性成熟；雌魚相信要最少15歲才達至性成熟。一項研究雌魚在9-12歲就開始卵發育，但卻直至15歲才性成熟。[[繁殖|繁殖]]並非每年都進行，差不多每三年才產一次卵，或更長的十年。<ref name="Keenlyne1">{{cite journal en|last=Keenlyne|first=K.D.|coauthors=L.G. Jenkins|title=Age at Sexual Maturity of the Pallid Sturgeon|journal=American Fisheries Society|volume=122|issue=3|pages=393–6|publisher=American Fisheries Society|url=http://afs.allenpress.com/perlserv/?request=get-abstract&doi=10.1577%2F1548-8659(1993)122%3C0393:AASMOT%3E2.3.CO%3B2|accessdate=2008-11-19|doi=10.1577/1548-8659(1993)122<0393:AASMOT>2.3.CO;2|date=May 1993}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="Recovery">{{cite web|title=Pallid Sturgeon: The Road to Recovery|publisher=U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service|date=July 15, 2008|url=http://www.fws.gov/YellowstoneRiverCoordinator/pallidsturgeon.html|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2009-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090514192623/http://www.fws.gov/yellowstonerivercoordinator/pallidsturgeon.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>牠們會於5-7月間產卵。<ref name="Kallemeyn"/>

在[[密蘇里河|密蘇里河]]建築堤壩前，淺色鱘魚會往上游遷徙<ref name="McKean">{{cite web|last=McKean|first=Andrew|title=A Whisker Away from Winking Out|publisher=Montana Outdoors|date=May/June 2006|url=http://fwp.mt.gov/mtoutdoors/HTML/articles/2006/pallidsturgeon.htm|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2008-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081108024026/http://fwp.mt.gov/mtoutdoors/HTML/articles/2006/pallidsturgeon.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在岩石或堅硬面產數十萬計的卵。<ref name="Kallemeyn">{{cite journal en|last=Kallemeyn|first=Larry|title=Status of the Pallid Sturgeon ''Scaphirhynchus albus''|journal=Fisheries|volume=8|pages=3–9|publisher=American Fisheries Society|year=1983|url=http://afs.allenpress.com/perlserv/?request=get-pdf&doi=10.1577%2F1548-8446%281983%29008%3C0003%3ASOTPS%3E2.0.CO%3B2|accessdate=2008-11-19|doi=10.1577/1548-8446(1983)008<0003:SOTPS>2.0.CO;2}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>在上密蘇里河曾捕獵一尾雌魚，估計就懷有17萬顆卵，佔體重11%。<ref name="Keenlyne2">{{cite journal en|last=Keenlyne|first=K.D.|coauthors=E. M. Grossman and L.G. Jenkins|title=Fecundity of the Pallid Sturgeon|journal=American Fisheries Society|volume=121|issue=1|pages=139–140|publisher=American Fisheries Society|url=http://afs.allenpress.com/perlserv/?request=get-abstract&doi=10.1577%2F1548-8659(1992)121%3C0139%3AFOTPS%3E2.3.CO%3B2&ct=1|accessdate=2008-11-19|doi=10.1577/1548-8659(1992)121<0139:FOTPS>2.3.CO;2|date=January 1992}}</ref>在受精後，魚卵在5-8日就會孵化<ref name="NRCS"/>，魚苗會用幾星期回到下游。當魚苗長尾巴後，牠們會游到慢流的水域生活。<ref name="McKean"/>魚苗的生存率極低，雖然有數十萬顆卵產下，也只有小量的可以成長。<ref name="Burton"/>

縛十年來，捕獵的淺色鱘魚都只是較年長的，故相信很久沒有自然繁殖。但於1990年代末，在下密蘇里河的河岸區發現了幼魚，是50年以來的第一次。<ref name="Burton"/>於2007年，發現有兩尾雌魚在[[密蘇里河國家娛樂區|密蘇里河國家娛樂區]]（Missouri National Recreational River）產卵。<ref name="USGS">{{cite web|title=Sturgeon Research Update: Confirmed Pallid sturgeon Sturgeon Spawning in the Missouri River in 2007|publisher=U.S. Geological Survey|url=http://pubs.usgs.gov/fs/2007/3053/pdf/FS2007-3053.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-11-19|date=July 2007|archive-date=2008-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081117014510/http://pubs.usgs.gov/fs/2007/3053/pdf/FS2007-3053.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==生態==
===分佈===
淺色鱘魚以往分佈在整個[[密蘇里河|密蘇里河]]及[[密西西比河|密西西比河]]區域。不過，在上密西西比河很少見到牠們的蹤影，可能是在該區沒有適合的棲息地。現時牠們已被列為處於[[極危|極危]]狀況。<ref name="Louisiana">{{cite web|title=Pallid Sturgeon (''Scaphirhynchus albus'')|publisher=Louisiana Department of Wildlife and Fisheries|url=http://www.wlf.louisiana.gov/pdfs/experience/naturalheritage/rareanimal/Pallid_Sturgeon-Scaphirhynchus_albus.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225123602/http://www.wlf.louisiana.gov/pdfs/experience/naturalheritage/rareanimal/Pallid_Sturgeon-Scaphirhynchus_albus.pdf|archivedate=2009-02-25}}</ref>截至2008年，在其原有的分佈地仍可見到牠們，但數量卻已嚴重減少。由[[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]]至[[路易西安納州|路易西安納州]]的密蘇里河及密西西比河，與及路易西安納州的[[阿查費耶拉河|阿查費耶拉河]]都仍保有一些淺色鱘魚較年長的群落。<ref name="EPA"/>淺色鱘魚並未曾很普遍，追溯至最早發現的1905年，在下密蘇里河的所有鏟鱘中也只佔五分之一，在[[伊利諾河|伊利諾河]]（Illinois River）及密西西比河交匯處更只佔500分之一。<ref name="Grady">{{cite web|last=Grady|first=Joanne|coauthors=Jim Milligan|title=Pallid and Shovelnose Sturgeon in the Lower Missouri and Middle Mississippi Rivers|publisher=U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service|url=http://www.fws.gov/midwest/columbiafisheries/documents/MICRA_sturgeon_report.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-11-19|date=February 2001|archive-date=2009-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225123625/http://www.fws.gov/midwest/columbiafisheries/documents/MICRA_sturgeon_report.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>於1985年至2000年間，淺色鱘魚與其他鏟鱘的比例更下降至400或650分之一。1996年一項研究就確定只餘下6000-21000尾淺色鱘魚。<ref name="IUCN">{{cite web|title=''Scaphirhynchus albus''|work=The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species|publisher=International Union for Conservation of Nature and Natural Resources|year=2004|url=http://www.iucnredlist.org/search/details.php/19940/all|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2007-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070430210358/http://www.iucnredlist.org/search/details.php/19940/all|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===棲息地===
淺色鱘魚喜歡棲息在中至湍急的流域，大部份捕捉到的淺色鱘魚都是在水流秒速0.10-0.88米的河區。牠們也喜歡生活在混濁的水域及水淨介乎0.91-7.6米。牠們一般會在砂質及岩石河床出沒。

在淺色鱘魚身上植入發訊器可以追蹤其習性。研究發現牠們喜歡較闊的河流、河心沙洲及島嶼，而且一般在水深0.61-14米的地方生活。研究亦顯示牠們每日可以游21公里，時速達9.2公里。<ref name="Bramblett">{{cite journal en|last=Bramblett|first=Robert|coauthors=Robert White|title=Habitat Use and Movements of Pallid and Shovelnose Sturgeon in the Yellowstone and Missouri Rivers in Montana and North Dakota|journal=Transactions of the American Fisheries Society|volume=130|issue=6|pages=1006–25|publisher=American Fisheries Society|location=Bethesda, Maryland|year=2001|accessdate=2008-11-19|doi=10.1577/1548-8659(2001)130<1006:HUAMOP>2.0.CO;2}}</ref>

===食性===
淺色鱘魚一般都是底棲的，在[[河流|河流]]底部覓食。雖然現時對牠們的食性所知甚少，但相信牠們是機會主義者。<ref name="EPA"/>從幼魚的[[胃部|胃部]]發現牠們的食性會按季節變更。一些季節，牠們會吃不同的[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]；而在另一些季節，牠們則會吃不同的[[魚類|魚類]]。<ref name="Wanner">{{cite journal en|last=Wanner|first=Greg|coauthors=D. A. Shuman, and D. W. Willis|title=Food Habits of Juvenile Pallid Sturgeon and Adult Shovel nose Sturgeon in the Missouri River Downstream of Fort Randall Dam, South Dakota|journal=Journal of Freshwater Ecology|volume=22|issue=1|pages=81-92|publisher=Oikos Publishers|location=La Crosse, Wisconsin|url=http://wfs.sdstate.edu/wfsdept/Publications/Willis/439-F%20Pallid%20Shovelnose%20Sturgeon%20Wanner.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-11-19|date=March 2007|archive-date=2009-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225123602/http://wfs.sdstate.edu/wfsdept/Publications/Willis/439-F%20Pallid%20Shovelnose%20Sturgeon%20Wanner.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>牠們吃魚類較[[密西西比鏟鱘|密西西比鏟鱘]]多。<ref name="Iowa">{{cite web|title=Pallid Sturgeon|publisher=The Iowa Department of Natural Resources|url=http://www.iowadnr.com/fish/iafish/pallstur.html|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080706190348/http://www.iowadnr.com/fish/iafish/pallstur.html|archivedate=2008-07-06}}</ref><ref name="Wanner"/>82%的食物是魚類，其他的則是[[搖蚊|搖蚊]]、[[蜉蝣|蜉蝣]]及[[毛翅目|毛翅目]]，與及小量的[[腐植質|腐植質]]及[[植物|植物]]。<ref name="Wilson">{{cite web|last=Wilson|first=Ryan|title=Pallid Sturgeon Recovery Update|publisher=U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service|date=April 2004|url=http://www.fws.gov/mountain-prairie/MissouriRiver/Pallid_Update_04.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-12-06|archive-date=2009-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090109075420/http://www.fws.gov/mountain-prairie/missouririver/Pallid_Update_04.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==保育狀況==
[[File:Pallid_Sturgeon_released_1999.jpg|right]]。]]
雖然淺色鱘魚並未普遍，但於20世紀末其數量大幅減少，於1996年牠們更被列為[[瀕危|瀕危]]。<ref name="NRCS"/>[[美國政府|美國政府]]及大部份州份都已開展了保育淺色鱘魚的計劃。淺色鱘魚的野生[[繁殖|繁殖]]在很多地區已很少有，故需要人工協助。<ref name="montana"/><ref name="Wildhaber">{{cite web|last=Wildhaber|first=Mark L.|coauthors=Aaron J. DeLonay, Diana M. Papoulias, David L. Galat, Robert B. Jacobson, Darin G. Simpkins, Patrick J. Braaten, Carl E. Korschgen, and Michael J. Mac|title=A Conceptual Life-History Model for Pallid and Shovelnose Sturgeon|publisher=U.S. Geological Survey|date=2007|url=http://www.uwyo.edu/enr/ienr/PSWorkshop2007/circ_1315.pdf|format=pdf|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2009-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225123608/http://www.uwyo.edu/enr/ienr/PSWorkshop2007/circ_1315.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>釣獲淺色鱘魚以往是一種獎狀，但現今既不准漁獵，捕獲後更要放生到水中。牠們是可供食用的，且非常可口；雌魚的[[魚子|魚子]]則可以製成[[魚子醬|魚子醬]]。<ref name="Guide"/>

在[[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]]、[[內布拉斯加州|內布拉斯加州]]、[[北達科他州|北達科他州]]及[[南達科他州|南達科他州]][[大平原|大平原]]的密蘇里河河道及環境已被大幅改變。運河化及建築堤壩阻礙了淺色鱘魚的上游遷徙。水流減少及沉積令區內的氾濫平原不再有季節性的氾濫。自1937年建造[[派克堡大壩|派克堡大壩]]（Fort Peck Dam）以來，密蘇里河就有超過90%的[[濕地|濕地]]及沙洲消失。密蘇里河超過3219公里的環境因而被改變，只餘下大壩上游的環境被保存下來。<ref name="Power">{{cite web|last=Power|first=Greg|title=The Missouri River System's "Other" Fish|publisher=U. S. Geological Survey|date=2006|url=http://www.npwrc.usgs.gov/resource/fish/othrfish/overview.htm|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080917075113/http://www.npwrc.usgs.gov/resource/fish/othrfish/overview.htm|archivedate=2008-09-17}}</ref>這種改變令很多當地的魚類受到嚴重打擊。在13個淺色鱘魚出沒的州份，只有少量的其他魚類被列為瀕危。<ref name="Tess">{{cite web|title=How many species are listed in each state (based on published population data)?|work=Threatened & Endangered Species System|publisher=U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service|date=2008|url=http://ecos.fws.gov/tess_public/StateListing.do?state=all|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061207200043/http://ecos.fws.gov/tess_public/StateListing.do?state=all|archivedate=2006-12-07}}</ref>雖然現已投放了很多資源在保育工作上，但由於淺色鱘魚只有很少自給自足的群落，故相信還要數十年的時間來進行保育。

===保育工作===
在[[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]][[密蘇里河|密蘇里河]]及[[黃石河|黃石河]]的兩個淺色鱘魚群落正面臨[[滅絕|滅絕]]的危險，估計這兩個群落於2018年就會消失。<ref name="montana"/>雖然自1996年已投放了很多資源在保育工作上，但要待雌魚15年的性成熟期才得知其成效。[[美國墾務局|美國墾務局]]（U.S. Bureau of Reclamation）每4-5年就在[[台伯河大壩|台伯河大壩]]注入脈衝水，嘗試重造下游的氾濫平原，恢復淺色鱘魚的棲息地。<ref name="montana2">{{cite web|title=Pallid Sturgeon — ''Scaphirhynchus albus''|publisher=State of Montana|url=http://fieldguide.mt.gov/detail_AFCAA02010.aspx|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2008-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080924143215/http://fieldguide.mt.gov/detail_AFCAA02010.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[Image:Radio_transmitter_implant_in_pallid_sturgeon.jpg|right]]

在[[內布拉斯加州|內布拉斯加州]][[普拉特河|普拉特河]]（Platte River）下游捕獵了小量的淺色鱘魚。普拉特河不像[[密西西比河|密西西比河]]及密蘇里河，只有少數的堤壩，可以從密西西比河的合流點往上游。下普拉特河的水深較淺，有大量的沙洲及小洲。雖然淺色鱘魚較喜歡湍流及深水[[河流|河流]]，但於1979年至2003年間，就在普拉特河發現了超過十幾條淺色鱘魚。<ref name="Platte2">{{cite book en|last=Committee on Endangered and Threatened Species in the Platte River Basin|title=Endangered and Threatened Species of the Platte River|publisher=The National Academies Press|date=2004|location=Washington, D. C.|pages=225–239|url=http://books.nap.edu/openbook.php?record_id=10978&page=225|id=ISBN 978-0-309-09230-2|access-date=2009-11-15|archive-date=2011-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607070310/http://books.nap.edu/openbook.php?record_id=10978&page=225|dead-url=no}}</ref>這些淺色鱘魚都被植入了發訊器來追蹤牠們的行蹤，以了解適合的水深及水流情況。大部份在普拉特河的淺色鱘魚都是於[[春天|春天]]及初夏捕捉到的。到了仲夏，由於水深減少及水流減慢，淺色鱘魚會回到密蘇里河。

由[[麋鹿角河|麋鹿角河]]（Elkhorn River）延伸至密蘇里河交匯處的一段長48公里的普拉特河下游，有適合淺色鱘魚產卵的地方，不過未有證據牠們曾於此地方產卵。<ref name="Platte2"/>下普拉特河及下黃石河都是適合淺色鱘魚自然[[繁殖|繁殖]]的候選地方。<ref name="Billings"/>為了建立棲息地，於[[加文斯波因特大壩|加文斯波因特大壩]]（Gavins Point Dam）也有注入脈衝水的計劃，對淺色鱘魚產卵有一定的幫助。<ref name="Herald">{{cite news|last=Hendee|first=David|title=Missouri River plan calls for '09 water pulses|publisher=Omaha World Herald|date=October 3, 2009|accessdate=2008-11-19}}</ref> 
於1998年在[[密蘇里州|密蘇里州]][[大馬迪國家漁業和野生動物保護區|大馬迪國家漁業和野生動物保護區]]（Big Muddy National Fish & Wildlife Refuge）發現了淺色鱘魚的魚苗，是50年以來第一次發現的野生魚苗。產卵的位點是一條為提供適合棲息地而發展的側道。<ref name="Ikenson">{{cite news|last=Ikenson|first=Ben|title=Biologists struggle to keep the pallid sturgeon from going extinct|work=Reviving the Missouri River's dinosaur|publisher=ESPN|date=May 31, 2006|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/outdoors/general/columns/story?columnist=guest_columnist&page=c_col_Ikenson_sturgeon_pallid|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721212740/http://sports.espn.go.com/outdoors/general/columns/story?columnist=guest_columnist&page=c_col_Ikenson_sturgeon_pallid|dead-url=no}}</ref>這條側道成為了淺色鱘魚魚苗避開密蘇里河急流的地方。<ref name="Mississippi">{{cite web|title=Pallid Sturgeon, ''Scaphirhynchus albus''|publisher=Mississippi Interstate Cooperative Resource Association|url=http://wwwaux.cerc.cr.usgs.gov/MICRA/PALLIDST.HTM|accessdate=2008-11-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081007185220/http://wwwaux.cerc.cr.usgs.gov/micra/PALLIDST.HTM|archivedate=2008-10-07}}</ref>

